<div class="patternContent"><div class="patternTopic"> <h1><a name="North_Carolina_Grid_School_OSG_C"></a>  North Carolina Grid School  / OSG Campus and National Cyberinfrastructure Workshop </h1>
<p />
 <font color="#0000ff"> <strong>April 22-23, 2009</strong> at <strong>RENCI, North Carolina</strong> </font>
<p />
<!--
<a href="https://twiki.opensciencegrid.org/twiki/pub/Education/ASP2016/NCGS09/MWGS08_Announcement.pdf" target="_top">print out the flyer</a>
-->
<p />
<font color="#ff0000"> Please do not forget to bring your <strong>laptop</strong> with you for NCGS09!
</font>
<p />
<table>
<tr>
<td width=40%>
